#

Savory Stuffed Bell Peppers

$12.5
350 kcal
Difficulty: 30%

Allergens:

NutsDairy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Tags:

VegetarianComfort FoodBakedHealthy

Description

Colorful bell peppers filled with a savory mixture of rice, black beans, corn, and spices, baked until tender.

Ingredients

  • Bell Peppers: 4 large
  • Cooked Rice: 1 cup
  • Black Beans (canned): 1 can
  • Corn (canned or frozen): 1 cup
  • Diced Tomatoes (canned): 1 can
  • Cheddar Cheese (shredded): 1 cup
  • Cumin: 1 tsp
  • Paprika: 1 tsp
  • Olive Oil: 1 tbsp
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black Pepper: to taste
